WEBVTT

00:06.938 --> 00:09.038
VANESSA: <i>Last season
on</i> Penny Dreadful...

00:09.038 --> 00:11.356
<i>Do you believe the past can return?</i>

00:11.492 --> 00:12.973
SEMBENE: <i>It never leaves us.</i>

00:12.998 --> 00:14.017
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)

00:14.398 --> 00:16.332
<i>It is who we are.</i>

00:18.424 --> 00:21.041
VANESSA: <i>When Lucifer fell,
he did not fall alone.</i>

00:21.066 --> 00:24.293
One brother to Earth
and the other to Hell.

00:24.317 --> 00:25.426
- (SCREECHING)
- (GASPING)

00:25.619 --> 00:28.609
Both in an eternal quest
for the Mother of Evil.

00:29.053 --> 00:31.823
VANESSA: <i>You'll understand I
find it difficult to accept</i>

00:32.030 --> 00:34.592
I'm the object of an
eternal satanic quest.

00:34.617 --> 00:36.657
JOAN: <i>You have to learn
to protect yourself.</i>

00:37.204 --> 00:40.396
They will hunt you
until the end of days.

00:40.421 --> 00:41.451
(GROWLING)

00:42.918 --> 00:43.927
MADAME KALI: <i>She has a protector.</i>

00:43.928 --> 00:45.159
(HECATE) Lupus Dei.

00:45.422 --> 00:46.748
<i>And he is powerful.</i>

00:46.835 --> 00:49.977
Mr. Chandler? Inspector
Bartholomew Rusk.

00:50.002 --> 00:52.485
We've had some trouble here in London.
Murders.

00:52.510 --> 00:53.897
(GROWLING)

00:53.898 --> 00:54.937
(WHISPERING) I know you're involved.

00:54.938 --> 00:55.938
And your proof?

00:55.939 --> 00:57.977
<i>I'll find it. I always find it.</i>

00:57.978 --> 00:59.917
Lily, you must come home.

00:59.918 --> 01:00.927
I love you.

01:01.087 --> 01:02.236
I am home, darling.

01:02.391 --> 01:03.977
When our day has come...

01:03.978 --> 01:06.266
you will know terror.

01:06.354 --> 01:08.889
MADAME KALI: She's the one
the Master seeks above all.

01:09.008 --> 01:10.077
End the torment, Vanessa.

01:10.078 --> 01:12.749
Be who you were meant to be.

01:12.898 --> 01:14.879
I know what I am.

01:15.022 --> 01:16.944
(YELLING)

01:17.048 --> 01:18.067
(ETHAN GROWLING)

01:18.558 --> 01:20.559
(HECATE) <i>The Wolf of God.</i>

01:20.584 --> 01:23.007
Stand alongside the great winged Lucifer

01:23.008 --> 01:24.978
<i>as he reconquers heaven's bloody throne.</i>

01:27.597 --> 01:29.556
I belong away from mankind.

01:29.581 --> 01:31.475
When you have stood in
blood long enough...

01:31.690 --> 01:32.967
<i>what is there left?</i>

01:32.968 --> 01:34.913
VANESSA: <i>Sir Malcolm is going to Africa.</i>

01:34.938 --> 01:36.610
This dreadful house will soon be empty.

01:36.724 --> 01:38.752
We can lock the doors
and walk away forever.

01:38.928 --> 01:39.928
Walk with me.

01:39.929 --> 01:41.977
There's no walking away from what I am.

01:41.978 --> 01:44.203
- You'll confess?
- Yes.

01:44.295 --> 01:46.235
RUSK: It's an extradition order.

01:46.713 --> 01:48.723
You're going home, Ethan.

01:48.898 --> 01:49.928
ETHAN: <i>Dear Vanessa...</i>

01:50.402 --> 01:52.886
<i>your many kindnesses I
will always carry with me.</i>

01:53.045 --> 01:54.675
<i>But I am made for the dark.</i>

01:54.763 --> 01:57.047
<i>Your road may be difficult.</i>

01:57.048 --> 01:58.688
<i>But mine is doomed.</i>

01:59.594 --> 02:00.908
<i>So we walk alone.</i>

02:04.409 --> 02:06.329
So we walk alone.

02:07.968 --> 02:09.918
<i>♪</i>

02:12.591 --> 02:16.194
