56:13.287 --> 56:17.217
THE MASTER: Have no fear, child.

56:18.327 --> 56:20.267
Look at me.

56:22.247 --> 56:24.277
Look at me.

56:32.227 --> 56:35.197
Tell me about her.

56:36.327 --> 56:41.277
She you call Vanessa Ives.

56:43.247 --> 56:46.156
I don't know anything!
I don't know anything!

56:46.157 --> 56:50.337
You will learn more and inform me.

56:52.217 --> 56:56.217
You will open her secrets to me.

56:57.367 --> 57:01.176
Tell me your name.

57:01.177 --> 57:02.267
My name...

57:03.267 --> 57:07.147
(GULPING) My name is Renfield.

57:09.347 --> 57:12.267
Bend your head back.

57:13.197 --> 57:15.347
Give me your neck.

57:18.207 --> 57:21.226
Give me your throat.

57:21.227 --> 57:22.267
(CRYING)

57:27.317 --> 57:29.207
